{
  "stem": "19969.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They work-- they did all the dirty work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And talking to the prison who was with me, he explained to me that they did all the dirty work.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're the ones that had to handle the bodies, put them in the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they got more-- better food than the ones inside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know how many there were, but there-- probably a dozen or more.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I saw four or five.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were outside and they were all in pretty good physical shape as contrasted to the ones that were inside, who hardly anybody weighed more than 90 pounds, let's say, just skin and bone.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, this one guy, this was prisoner I had, took me around and showed me some aspects of the camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He showed me an area where there was a-- --some boards like latticework over a pile of-- over some sand.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he got down and explained to me how the Germans executed-- not-- many German officers, he said.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Sometime before we arrived, they made them get down and put their heads down and they put a bullet in the back of their head.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Apparently--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, apparently, that was the residue of the attack on Hitler.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, they didn't know who to hold responsible for that attack on Hitler so they just picked out a bunch of people who were on the staff of a-- of a general who was one of the plotters.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of them came to Dachau and they were executed there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or anybody that they thought was wanting to give up at the last minute were executed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "These were German officers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were the only ones, so the prisoner told me, that were executed in that manner.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
